headline: Ken Washington appointed to TE Connectivity board of directors
summary: The board of directors of TE Connectivity plc (NYSE: TEL), a world leader in connectors and sensors, has appointed Ken Washington to the board, effective November 17, 2025.

headline: Quanterix Corporation (QTRX) Reports Q3 Loss, Tops Revenue Estimates
summary: Quanterix (QTRX) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -56.52% and +4.18%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: Looking at the Changing Story for Medtronic After Analyst Upgrades and Board Shakeup
summary: Medtronic stock has seen its price target updated, with key financial assumptions reflecting both the company’s stable outlook and a slightly higher perception of risk. Improving analyst sentiment has supported this shift, as optimism grows around Medtronic’s product pipeline and strategic priorities.
